If you intend to change prop passed down to child assign it first to child data.

    &lt;template&gt;
      &lt;div&gt;
        &lt;input v-model=&quot;name&quot; placeholder=&quot;string&quot;&gt;
        &lt;input v-model=&quot;number&quot; placeholder=&quot;number&quot;&gt;
